data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home on a large lot in Pine Tree ISD! Home features, 3 spacious bedrooms, cedar closets adding natural freshness to your storage space, a family room, eat in kitchen/dining room, and a versatile bonus room that could be transformed into a home office, playroom, or whatever suits your needs. Outside you will find mature trees and a neighboring creek, which runs right along the back edge of the property line. While this property requires a little TLC, it offers a canvas for your creativity and vision. Make your appointment today to see what this property has to offer!
